## Project Understanding

FolkCoder is two things:

1. **A web presence** (folkcoder.com) — a social platform where
   developers find hackathon teammates, discover events, showcase
   projects, and access structured curricula like SwarmPod.

2. **An AI-centered business infrastructure** — the backend systems,
   tooling, and workflows (powered by AI) that manage the business
   FolkCoder generates: user onboarding, content delivery, community
   management, partner/sponsor coordination.

SwarmPod (swarmpod-core) is the first featured framework on the
platform. It provides one-command Rails app scaffolding with
multi-repo architecture, Docker, and secrets management baked in.
The SwarmPod curriculum is the initial content funnel that drives
developers from localhost to FolkCoder registration.

